description:
Total supply - only 1000 1-1 characters by 1 artist - [Madebyrvk](https://www.instagram.com/madebyrvk) made.
Anime Punks™ are the dopest AnimePunks collection. [History of APs.](https://medium.com/@shikamarunft/anime-punks-fd581b25f68)
Each character is a originally hand drawn unique pixel art image parody. Non generated collection.
Every series has unique background color.
Start Prices:
Common character 0.09 
Legendary character 0.49 (special forms)
Paying homage to the OG punks and all Manga Artists (漫画家).
[Unofficial Punks](https://opensea.io/assets?search[sortAscending]=false&search[sortBy]=CREATED_DATE&search[stringTraits][0][name]=Certified&search[stringTraits][0][values][0]=Unofficial%20Punks)
